1. U ovome nema nikakvog *smisla*. (There is no *sense* in this.)
2. Molim te, objasni mi *smisao* ove igre. (Please explain to me the *meaning* of this game.)
3. Ona je u potpunom *smislu* te reči bila srećna. (She was happy in every *sense* of the word.)
4. Ne vidim *smisao* ovog razgovora. (I don't see the *point* of this conversation.)
5. Bez *smisla* je trošiti novac na nešto što neće koristiti nikome. (It's *meaningless* to spend money on something that won't benefit anyone.)
6. Tvoje ponašanje nema nikakvog *smisla* u ovom kontekstu. (Your behavior makes no *sense* in this context.)
7. *Smisao* života je pitanje na koje mnogi traže odgovor. (The *meaning* of life is a question that many seek to answer.)
8. Ova knjiga ima dublji *smisao* od samog zapleta. (This book has a deeper *meaning* than just the plot.)
9. Bez obzira na to koliko puta ponovimo istu stvar, *smisao* ostaje isti. (No matter how many times we repeat the same thing, the *meaning* remains the same.)
10. Uspjeh nema *smisla* bez truda. (Success makes no *sense* without effort.)